data.description: Welcome to this charming two-story residence with a solar-heated pool – a true homecoming experience. Recently upgraded with a new roof in June 2023, this property boasts ample living space, perfect for your entire family. With 3 bedrooms, 2.5 baths, and over 2,050 SF of living area, it provides a spacious and comfortable environment. The versatile open floor plan encompasses a family room, dining area, and a generously sized kitchen, complete with a fabulous breakfast bar island. Ascending to the second floor, you'll discover a master suite, two guest bedrooms, and an additional full bathroom. A flexible loft space awaits, ideal for a second family room, den, playroom, or convertible to a fourth guest bedroom. The expansive master bedroom features an ensuite spa with a Jacuzzi tub, (2) pedestal sinks, a private water closet, and a separate walk-in shower. Step outside to the private backyard, which is generously sized and fully fenced. The pool deck and open patio, crafted from decorative pavers, create an inviting outdoor space. The well-designed pool includes a deep-end seating bench and swim-out. The spacious lanai, with an insulated ceiling and fan, is fully screened-in for your comfort. Practical features include a generator power outlet for emergency preparedness, while built-in storage shelves in the garage facilitate organization. Check out all the great nature trails, bike paths, and recreational facilities that Palm Coast has to offer! Don't miss the opportunity to schedule your private showing and explore the unique charm of this home today.
